'''Copper Captain''' is a term for a [[Brummagem]] captain; a ''[[General von Poffenburgh]]''. 

[[Michael Perez]] is so called in the play [[Rule a Wife and Have a Wife]].

[[Washington Irving]] wrote, "To this copper-captain was confided the command of the troops."


